videos.description: Brett Rypien throws a 15-yard dart to Sean Modster for the first Boise State touchdown of the night.
videos.headline: Rypien throws dart to Modster for 15-yard TD

videos.description: Brett Rypien connects with Sean Modster for a 16-yard touchdown pass to put Boise State on top of New Mexico 14-0.
videos.headline: Rypien throws pinpoint pass to Modster for TD

videos.description: Desmond Williams rips the ball free from Zahneer Shuler and returns it 9 yards for a Boise State touchdown.
videos.headline: Boise State defense forces fumble, scores TD

videos.description: Sean Modster receives the pass and stretches out to hit the pylon and score the touchdown for Boise State.
videos.headline: Modster stretches out for third TD

videos.description: Marcus Hayes returns a punt 86 yards for a New Mexico touchdown, the first punt return for a touchdown for the Lobos in 16 years.
videos.headline: Hayes returns punt 86 yards for Lobos TD
